name: I Surf The Net
tagline: I surf the net. Do you?
body:
### Welcome to surfing the net.
When I learned this domain was open I bought it right away.  I don't what I want to do with it yet, or if I'll keep it.  If you have an idea let me know on github. https://github.com/ISurfThe

This domain is also currently for sale here: https://flippa.com/7057605-isurfthe-net
